Texts.Eng: I've arrived at an ^orange;Ancient Vault^white;! I wonder what secrets these ruins hide? I think I should take a look around...

The winds whisper of what you have done - you have ventured far, young one. But there are still doors you have yet to open. ^green;I can trade ^orange;keys^green; with you^white;, if you wish to ^green;open the ^orange;Ancient Gates^green; scattered among the stars^white;.
